013 bass guitar, rhythm guitar (uncredited)\n\n===Additional musicians===\n* [[Matt Walker (drummer)|Matt Walker]]&nbsp;\u2013 drums on \"To Sheila\", \"Ava Adore\", \"Daphne Descends\", \"Tear\", \"The Tale of Dusty and Pistol Pete\", \"Annie-Dog\", and \"Behold! The Night Mare\"\n* [[Matt Cameron]]&nbsp;\u2013 drums on \"For Martha\"\n* [[Joey Waronker]]&nbsp;\u2013 drums on \"[[Perfect (The Smashing Pumpkins song)|Perfect]]\", additional drums on \"Once Upon a Time\" and \"Pug\"\n* [[Dennis Flemion]]&nbsp;\u2013 additional vocals in \"To Sheila\" and \"Behold! The Night Mare\"\n* [[Jimmy Flemion]]&nbsp;\u2013 additional vocals in \"To Sheila\" and \"Behold! The Night Mare\"\n* [[Bon Harris]]&nbsp;\u2013 additional [[Programming (music)|programming]] on tracks 2, 3, 4, 5, 7, 8, 9, and 13; additional vocals in \"For Martha\"\n* [[Brad Wood]]&nbsp;\u2013 additional production and engineering on tracks 1, 2, 4, 6, 13, and 15, additional vocals in \"Behold! The Night Mare\", [[Organ (music)|organ]] in \"Blank Page\"\n\n===Technical===\n{{div col}}\n* Robbie Adams&nbsp;\u2013 [[Audio engineering|engineering]], mixing\n* Chris Brickley&nbsp;\u2013 recording assistant\n* [[Flood (producer)|Flood]]&nbsp;\u2013 additional production, mixing\n* Eric Greedy&nbsp;\u2013 mix assistant\n* Steve Johnson&nbsp;\u2013 recording assistant\n* Ron Lowe&nbsp;\u2013 recording assistant\n* Jay Nicholas&nbsp;\u2013 mix assistant\n* Frank Olinsky&nbsp;\u2013 art direction and design\n* Neil Perry&nbsp;\u2013 engineer, mixing\n* Matt Prock&nbsp;\u2013 recording assistant\n* Chris Shepard&nbsp;\u2013 engineer\n* Jamie Siegel&nbsp;\u2013 mix assistant\n* [[Bjorn Thorsrud]]&nbsp;\u2013 digital editing, engineering\n* Ed Tinley&nbsp;\u2013 recording assistant\n* Andy Van Dette&nbsp;\u2013 digital editing and compilation\n* Jeff Vereb&nbsp;\u2013 recording assistant\n* [[Howie Weinberg]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Audio mastering|mastering]]\n* Howard C. Willing&nbsp;\u2013 engineering, mix assistant\n* John Wydrycs&nbsp;\u2013 mix assistant\n* [[Yelena Yemchuk]]&nbsp;\u2013 photography, art direction and design\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|Chart (1998)\n!scope=\"col\"|Peak<br/>position\n|-\n{{albumchart|Australia|1|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Austria|7|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|1|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|8|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|BillboardCanada|2|artist=Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n|Danish Albums ([[Hitlisten]])<ref name=\"Listen\">{{cite news |title=Listen - Danmarks Officielle Hitliste - Udarbejdet af AIM Nielsen for IFPI Danmark - Uge 24 |work=[[Ekstra Bladet]] |location=[[Copenhagen]] |language=Danish |date=1998-06-14}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|4\n\n|-\n{{albumchart|Netherlands|5|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Finland|5|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|France|1|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Germany4|3|id=2773|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|New Zealand|1|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Norway|1|artist=The Smashing Pumpkins|album=Adore|accessdate=February 8, 2014}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Scottish Albums ([[Official Charts Company|OCC]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/charts/scottish-albums-chart/19980607/40/|title=Official Scottish Albums Chart Top 100|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=February 17, 2013}}</ref>\n|align=\